  <NodeName>k__BackingField: DialogueName11
  <Choices>k__BackingField:
  - <Text>k__BackingField: Hang out more with rother rich folks?
    <NextDialogue>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 78fd503a1037dc94c935d1955f2b5a72, type: 2}
  - <Text>k__BackingField: The school teaches them like everyone else?
    <NextDialogue>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: a6a958d12a5eb594abfc63b9ef717e0d, type: 2}
  - <Text>k__BackingField: I don't know
    <NextDialogue>k__BackingField: {fileID: 11400000, guid: ad7548f3225e1134290bc9f9f67702a8, type: 2}
  <IsStartingDialogue>k__BackingField: 0
  <Text>k__BackingField: Okay, but not all wealthy Americans necessarily share liberal
    values of masculinity at the start, even if they have the choice to do so. How
    can going to university influence them?
